prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, hilariously attempting to blow out a single, very resilient birthday candle on a cupcake that's precariously balanced on its belly. The sloth has a look of comical concentration and puffed-out cheeks. Floating around the sloth are whimsical, colorful party confetti shapes. Centered below the sloth, in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday". The entire scene is rendered as a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brushstrokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures.
